  title: Broken Heater
  bodyText: A tired woman from Room 117 speaks in the slow, strained voice of someone
    awakened by discomfort. She says the heater has been blowing cold air for over
    an hour. Her husband is sick, their daughter is crying, and the room feels colder
    than outside.
